  "decision_conditions": [
    "The proposed single storey rear extension does not constitute permitted development by virtue of the provisions of Class A, Schedule 2, Part 1 of the Town and Country Planning (General Permitted Development) (England) Order 2015 (as amended) because the proposed extension would adjoin a wall which is deemed to be a side wall therefore the proposed extension would not be considered to be be a rear extension assessed under GPDO provisions for larger householder extensions. Rather the proposal would constitute a single storey side extension that exceeds more than half the width of the original dwelling house. On this basis, the prior approval application is refused."
